{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/lepBanner.png?t=1736960280\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>LiDAR Exploration Program</strong> is an atmospheric horror adventure game where you can't see the world around you. Use the lidar scanner to colorize everything around you. The game contains several levels to explore, in each of which you have to scan unknown objects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPLORE AND SCAN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/ForestScan.gif?t=1736960280\" />You find yourself in complete darkness, in which you can't see anything, but thanks to the scanner you can find your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SCAN UNKNOWN OBJECTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/ObjectScan.gif?t=1736960280\" />To You will have to look for objects, some of them will be ordinary, and some will seem very strange and creepy. Using the scanner you will be able to explore them.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">USE MAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/Map.gif?t=1736960280\" />You can use a map that shows the environment from above. With its help you can find the very objects that need to be scanned.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">8 LEVELS AVAILABLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/LevelSelector.gif?t=1736960280\" />You have to explore 8 different locations in each of which you have to look for objects. You can explore the forest, cave, abandoned city and other locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p